0,0,0,163151,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,36949),('I spotted an obelisk of ancient stone upon the high ridge.','',199152,0,0,1,0,0,163152,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,36949),('It did not seem important. The Jailer\'s forces pay it little heed. What do you think it is?','',199153,0,0,6,0,0,163153,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,36949),('','Our way out of here--we hope.',199154,0,0,5,0,0,0,163154,0,0,0,0,0,0,36949),('','Try to save her all you like. She has seen the truth!',199167,0,0,1,0,0,0,158235,0,0,0,0,0,0,36949),('','Our realm lies in ruins. The Forsworn will set us free!',199168,0,0,1,0,0,0,158237,0,0,0,0,0,0,36949),('','You were foolish to test a Paragon\'s might.',199169,0,0,1,0,0,0,158241,0,0,0,0,0,0,36949),('','I will know your truth!',199170,0,0,1,0,0,0,158242,0,0,0,0,0,0,36949),('','Your day will come. This is just the beginning!',199171,0,0,1,0,0,0,158243,0,0,0,0,0,0,36949),('','Now to finish this matter.',199172,0,0,1,0,0,0,158239,0,0,0,0,0,0,36949),('Highlord Fordragon! We have escaped the Maw. Thank you for your aid.','',199173,0,0,0,0,0,164924,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,36949),('I must return to Azeroth and tell our allies what we\'ve learned, father. But when duty allows it, I will stand once more at your side.','',199174,0,0,1,0,0,164922,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,36949),('','Our margrave has been slain, Ashbringer. The Chosen need your blade, now more than ever.',199177,0,0,1,0,0,0,165729,0,0,0,0,0,0,36949),('No... then my warning comes too late! We have been betrayed by one of our own!','',199178,0,0,1,0,0,165459,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,36949),('Draka! We must return to Maldraxxus at once. Margrave Krexus--','',199179,0,0,5,0,0,165458,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,36949),('There will be time for us to speak later, my son. I swear it.','',199180,0,0,1,0,0,164923,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,36949),('','We depart for Maldraxxus at once, $n. Vyraz will answer for his crimes.',199181,0,0,1,0,0,0,164921,0,0,0,0,0,0,36949),('Next, you will inflict suffering on anyone foolish enough to fight you.','',199204,0,0,0,64,0,159450,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,36949),('Agony and Corrupti